Package: eDNAnalyze
Title: Import, Annotate, and Visualize DNA Metabarcoding Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Cameron", "Walsh", email = "cajw@hawaii.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9567-6721"))
    person("Mykle", "Hoban", email = "mhoban@hawaii.edu", role = "ctb",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2514-3599")))
Description: Manage and augment taxonomic assignment data provided by a DNA
    metabarcoding bioinformatic pipeline (typically a version of eDNAFlow)
    sorted by operational taxonomic unit (OTU). Generate text reports and plots
    of read and OTU abundance for each sample and across the entire dataset.
